<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id126348f8-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777" identifier="/us/usc/t44/s4104"><num value="4104">§ 4104.</num><heading> Definition</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this chapter, the term “Federal electronic information” means Federal public information stored electronically.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id126348f9-e3ef-11ef-8e9f-f6e47fd25777">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/103/40/s2/a">Pub. L. 103–40, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1993-06-08">June 8, 1993</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/107/113">107 Stat. 113</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
